Behind the Brand

Claudia
del Castillo

A Rhode Island School of Design alum, Claudia has over a decade 's experience at Reebok curating concepts for apparel and footwear design. She founded Chipie Design over ten years ago and set out to brand-up Cape Cod 's image one small business at a time.

Vinnie Arnone

He is the ultimate secret   weapon to add on to any project. Vinnie is a brand builder himself and an   illustrator extraordinaire. He graduated from the School of Museum of Fine Arts and started his career in NYC creating apparel graphics for Old Navy. He then expanded his experience to footwear at Reebok and bicycle graphic design at SE Bikes.

Christine
Stoliker

Our west coast liason, Christine is a gifted brand strategist that brings over a decade 's experience at Reebok setting the color and photography direction each season. She also brands small businesses in the San Diego area.
